 <br>
Under the new plan, a Mars mission probably is 15 years away, if not more. <br>
The interim focus will be on the Moon, which will help develop new technologies for a Mars mission. In the meantime, this new focus reduces the government sponsored emphasis on the Earth-orbit realm, helping to open it for private enterprise.  <br>
